<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>make leeway • make up leeway</xh5><p> <i>make leeway—</i>provide a margin of freedom, as of activity, time, or expenditure: Because we had to expand we had to get so much more machinery, so you <u>make leeway</u> for all this in the budget.</p><p> <i>make up leeway—</i>compensate that which has been lost or wasted (by doing extra work, etc.): There is a short break of ten minutes between each presentation, to <u>make up leeway</u> caused by prolonged discussion.</p> </entry>
